com.opengamma.strata.calc.marketdata.function

Class MissingDataAwareTimeSeriesProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.calc.marketdata.function.MissingDataAwareTimeSeriesProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimeSeriesProvider

    public final class MissingDataAwareTimeSeriesProvider
extends Object
implements TimeSeriesProvider
    Time series provider that handles data that can't be looked up because there was no market data rule for the calculation. It delegates to another provider for looking up time series.

    When there is no market data rule for a calculation, the ObservableId instances for the time series have the feed MarketDataFeed.NO_RULE. This builder creates failure results for those IDs and uses the delegate provider to provider the time series for the remaining IDs.
